        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CL for "the great book" [<hi rend="italic">Antiquity of man</hi> (1863)].</p> 
            <p>Richard Owen "ought to be ostracised by every Naturalist in England".</p>
            <p>CL’s book will "give the whole subject of change of species an enormous advance".</p>
        </abstract>
